flowchart TB
    A[Input SEM Image] --> B[Preprocess Resize MedianBlur CLAHE]
    B --> C[Tensor 1x256x256]

    subgraph UNet[Basic U-Net custom]
      C --> D1[Encoder Block1 DoubleConv]
      D1 --> P1[MaxPool]
      P1 --> D2[Encoder Block2 DoubleConv]
      D2 --> P2[MaxPool]
      P2 --> D3[Encoder Block3 DoubleConv]
      D3 --> P3[MaxPool]
      P3 --> BN[Bottleneck DoubleConv]
      BN --> U3[UpConv]
      U3 --> CAT3[Concat Skip3]
      CAT3 --> DC3[DoubleConv]
      DC3 --> U2[UpConv]
      U2 --> CAT2[Concat Skip2]
      CAT2 --> DC2[DoubleConv]
      DC2 --> U1[UpConv]
      U1 --> CAT1[Concat Skip1]
      CAT1 --> DC1[DoubleConv]
      DC1 --> OUT[1x1 Conv Logits]
    end

    OUT --> S[Sigmoid]
    S --> T[Threshold 0.4]
    T --> M[Predicted Mask]
    M --> N[Metrics and Visualization]
